We don't get a single penny.

00:51:25.920 --> 00:51:28.650
The volunteers that
also go once a year,

00:51:28.650 --> 00:51:30.330
they pay all their expenses.

00:51:30.330 --> 00:51:32.190
So every dollar you
donate are going

00:51:32.190 --> 00:51:34.890
to be used for the projects.

00:51:34.890 --> 00:51:38.910
I want to use this opportunity
to thank many, many Googlers

