00:52:16.650 --> 00:52:18.280
to this project.

00:52:18.280 --> 00:52:20.070
We are pretty picky,
because we want

00:52:20.070 --> 00:52:22.980
people that have
cultural sensitivity

00:52:22.980 --> 00:52:24.960
and that are really
compassionate.

00:52:24.960 --> 00:52:27.060
Being smart is
fantastic, but you've

00:52:27.060 --> 00:52:30.180
got to have the heart
as well as the brain.

00:52:30.180 --> 00:52:32.370
And you also have
to have patience

00:52:32.370 --> 00:52:33.690
and be willing to listen.

00:52:33.690 --> 00:52:35.110
And he's all of those things.

00:52:35.110 --> 00:52:36.590
So thank you very much.

00:52:36.590 --> 00:52:37.410
And thank you.

00:52:37.410 --> 00:52:38.890
This is wonderful being here.

00:52:38.890 --> 00:52:39.780
Thank you very much.

00:52:39.780 --> 00:52:41.724
RAFAEL: Thank you so much
for the inspiring talk.

00:52:41.724 --> 00:52:42.210
Thank you.

00:52:42.210 --> 00:52:43.501
MARIANNE KENT-STOLL: Thank you.

00:52:43.501 --> 00:52:45.126
